{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-tsx","path":"/blog/2021/vsmac-nuget-error/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"e03ff3fd-025a-503c-8c2c-70a26fb4316e","excerpt":"ある時 xUnit テストがしたかったのでテスト用のプロジェクトを作成したところ Nuget パッケージが復元できなくなってました。(もちろん更新もできません) 対処法 僕が最終的に解決した方法です。 ユーザー設定 > Nuget > ソース より以下のように「nuget.org…","html":"<p>ある時 xUnit テストがしたかったのでテスト用のプロジェクトを作成したところ Nuget パッケージが復元できなくなってました。(もちろん更新もできません)</p>\n<h2 id=\"対処法\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%AF%BE%E5%87%A6%E6%B3%95\" aria-label=\"対処法 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" height=\"16\" width=\"16\" style=\"display:inline-block; fill:#57606a;\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>対処法</h2>\n<p>僕が最終的に解決した方法です。</p>\n<p>ユーザー設定 > Nuget > ソース<br>\nより以下のように「nuget.org」以外のチェックボックスを外します。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 760px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d7afa063b656fd1e23724cf07ecff005/9ce1c/screenshot_VS-nuget_source.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 52.63157894736842%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"スクリーンショット_VS-nugetソース\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/d7afa063b656fd1e23724cf07ecff005/3c051/screenshot_VS-nuget_source.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d7afa063b656fd1e23724cf07ecff005/a2d4f/screenshot_VS-nuget_source.png 190w,\n/static/d7afa063b656fd1e23724cf07ecff005/3f520/screenshot_VS-nuget_source.png 380w,\n/static/d7afa063b656fd1e23724cf07ecff005/3c051/screenshot_VS-nuget_source.png 760w,\n/static/d7afa063b656fd1e23724cf07ecff005/b5cea/screenshot_VS-nuget_source.png 1140w,\n/static/d7afa063b656fd1e23724cf07ecff005/891d5/screenshot_VS-nuget_source.png 1520w,\n/static/d7afa063b656fd1e23724cf07ecff005/9ce1c/screenshot_VS-nuget_source.png 1886w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 760px) 100vw, 760px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>続いて Nuget を更新します。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 602px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/c03af587b5b7c42b2630cf154619050f/32056/screenshot_VS-nuget_update.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 41.05263157894738%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"スクリーンショット_VS-nuget更新\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/c03af587b5b7c42b2630cf154619050f/32056/screenshot_VS-nuget_update.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/c03af587b5b7c42b2630cf154619050f/a2d4f/screenshot_VS-nuget_update.png 190w,\n/static/c03af587b5b7c42b2630cf154619050f/3f520/screenshot_VS-nuget_update.png 380w,\n/static/c03af587b5b7c42b2630cf154619050f/32056/screenshot_VS-nuget_update.png 602w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 602px) 100vw, 602px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>少し待つと更新が完了します。<br>\n更新完了後 Nuget を復元すると xUnit が使えるようになりました。</p>\n<h2 id=\"その他にやったこと\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E3%81%9D%E3%81%AE%E4%BB%96%E3%81%AB%E3%82%84%E3%81%A3%E3%81%9F%E3%81%93%E3%81%A8\" aria-label=\"その他にやったこと permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" height=\"16\" width=\"16\" style=\"display:inline-block; fill:#57606a;\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>その他にやったこと</h2>\n<p>上記の方法に辿り着くまでにやったことを書いておきます。</p>\n<h3 id=\"キャッシュのクリア\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E3%82%AD%E3%83%A3%E3%83%83%E3%82%B7%E3%83%A5%E3%81%AE%E3%82%AF%E3%83%AA%E3%82%A2\" aria-label=\"キャッシュのクリア permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" height=\"16\" width=\"16\" style=\"display:inline-block; fill:#57606a;\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>キャッシュのクリア</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.fixes.pub/program/37041.html\">https://www.fixes.pub/program/37041.html</a></p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container default-dark\" data-language=\"bash\" data-index=\"0\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">$ nuget locals all -clear</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"色々更新\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E8%89%B2%E3%80%85%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0\" aria-label=\"色々更新 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" height=\"16\" width=\"16\" style=\"display:inline-block; fill:#57606a;\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>色々更新</h3>\n<p>僕は VS 関連を brew で入れてるのでアプデ。<br>\nCask は brew tap で入れてる便利なやつで。</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container default-dark\" data-language=\"bash\" data-index=\"1\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">$ brew update</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">$ brew upgrade</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">$ brew cu -a</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"nuget-v2-を追加してみる\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#nuget-v2-%E3%82%92%E8%BF%BD%E5%8A%A0%E3%81%97%E3%81%A6%E3%81%BF%E3%82%8B\" aria-label=\"nuget v2 を追加してみる permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" height=\"16\" width=\"16\" style=\"display:inline-block; fill:#57606a;\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Nuget v2 を追加してみる</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ranorex.techmatrix.jp/faq/%E3%83%91%E3%83%83%E3%82%B1%E3%83%BC%E3%82%B8%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E3%81%AB%E3%81%A6%E3%80%81nuget%E3%81%B8%E3%81%AE%E6%8E%A5%E7%B6%9A%E3%82%A8%E3%83%A9%E3%83%BC%E3%81%8C%E7%99%BA%E7%94%9F%E3%81%97//\">https://ranorex.techmatrix.jp/faq/パッケージ管理にて、nuget への接続エラーが発生し/</a></p>\n<p>ユーザー設定 > Nuget > ソース<br>\nにて「追加」より、</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container default-dark\" data-language=\"txt\" data-index=\"2\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">名前: nuget.org v2</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">ソース: https://www.nuget.org/api/v2/</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>を追加する。</p>\n<style class=\"grvsc-styles\">\n  .grvsc-container {\n    overflow: auto;\n    position: relative;\n    -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;\n    padding-top: 1rem;\n    padding-top: var(--grvsc-padding-top, var(--grvsc-padding-v, 1rem));\n    padding-bottom: 1rem;\n    padding-bottom: var(--grvsc-padding-bottom, var(--grvsc-padding-v, 1rem));\n    border-radius: 8px;\n    border-radius: var(--grvsc-border-radius, 8px);\n    font-feature-settings: normal;\n    line-height: 1.4;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-code {\n    display: table;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line {\n    display: table-row;\n    box-sizing: border-box;\n    width: 100%;\n    position: relative;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line > * {\n    position: relative;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-gutter-pad {\n    display: table-cell;\n    padding-left: 0.75rem;\n    padding-left: calc(var(--grvsc-padding-left, var(--grvsc-padding-h, 1.5rem)) / 2);\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-gutter {\n    display: table-cell;\n    -webkit-user-select: none;\n    -moz-user-select: none;\n    user-select: none;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-gutter::before {\n    content: attr(data-content);\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-source {\n    display: table-cell;\n    padding-left: 1.5rem;\n    padding-left: var(--grvsc-padding-left, var(--grvsc-padding-h, 1.5rem));\n    padding-right: 1.5rem;\n    padding-right: var(--grvsc-padding-right, var(--grvsc-padding-h, 1.5rem));\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-source:empty::after {\n    content: ' ';\n    -webkit-user-select: none;\n    -moz-user-select: none;\n    user-select: none;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-gutter + .grvsc-source {\n    padding-left: 0.75rem;\n    padding-left: calc(var(--grvsc-padding-left, var(--grvsc-padding-h, 1.5rem)) / 2);\n  }\n  \n  /* Line transformer styles */\n  \n  .grvsc-has-line-highlighting > .grvsc-code > .grvsc-line::before {\n    content: ' ';\n    position: absolute;\n    width: 100%;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line-diff-add::before {\n    background-color: var(--grvsc-line-diff-add-background-color, rgba(0, 255, 60, 0.2));\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line-diff-del::before {\n    background-color: var(--grvsc-line-diff-del-background-color, rgba(255, 0, 20, 0.2));\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line-number {\n    padding: 0 2px;\n    text-align: right;\n    opacity: 0.7;\n  }\n  \n  .default-dark {\n    background-color: #1E1E1E;\n    color: #D4D4D4;\n  }\n  .default-dark .mtk1 { color: #D4D4D4; }\n  .default-dark .grvsc-line-highlighted::before {\n    background-color: var(--grvsc-line-highlighted-background-color, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1));\n    box-shadow: inset var(--grvsc-line-highlighted-border-width, 4px) 0 0 0 var(--grvsc-line-highlighted-border-color, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5));\n  }\n</style>","fields":{"slug":"/blog/2021/vsmac-nuget-error/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"VisualStudio for Mac で Nugetの復元・更新ができない","description":null,"postdate":"2021-03-27T15:44:00","update":"2021-03-27T15:44:00","tags":["VisualStudio"]}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/blog/2021/vscode-theme-to-plug/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"VSCodeでテーマを設定→拡張機能へ"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/blog/2021/vscode-with-unitydiv/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"VSCodeでのUnity開発(MacOS)"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"e03ff3fd-025a-503c-8c2c-70a26fb4316e","previousPostId":"cc97ac7a-6ee2-56d1-97b3-c9907a068f47","nextPostId":"e3035d64-f688-57ed-96c2-aa4693cfbfdb"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3405293526","713408048"],"slicesMap":{}}